info.description:
HTSeq
=====

HTSeq is a Python library to facilitate processing and analysis of data
from high-throughput sequencing (HTS) experiments.

Documentation
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
http://htseq.readthedocs.io/en/master/index.html

Development
~~~~~~~~~~~
https://github.com/simon-anders/htseq
info.name: HTSeq
info.summary: A framework to process and analyze data from high-throughput sequencing (HTS) assays
